{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^system:QQ联系人:岛岛(2926855205)发来了消息:[图片]\n^system:20260304_091222:这张图片的内容是：7.2.4. 微分方程 y'sinx = y·lny 满足初始条件 y |_(x=π/2) = e 的特解为 ( ). (A) y = e^(sinx) (B) y = e^(tan(x/2))","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_091222"}
