{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^cyanAI:这道题选 B 哦！\n是分离变量法的题目呢。\n过程大概是这样：\n1. 分离变量：dy / (y * ln y) = dx / sin x\n2. 两边积分：\n   左边积出来是 ln|ln y|\n   右边积出来是 ln|tan(x/2)| + C\n3. 整理一下得到：ln y = C * tan(x/2)\n4. 代入初始条件 x=π/2, y=e，因为 tan(π/4)=1，ln e = 1，所以解得 C=1\n最后特解就是 y = e^(tan(x/2)) 啦。","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_091243"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^system:QQ联系人:岛岛(2926855205)发来了消息:lnlny咋积出来的？","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_091444"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^cyanAI:","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_091449"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^system:","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_091449"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^cyanAI:是用凑微分法哦！\n左边是 ∫ 1/(y * ln y) dy\n我们可以把 1/y 拿到 dy 里面去，因为 d(ln y) = (1/y) dy\n所以积分就变成了 ∫ 1/(ln y) d(ln y)\n这不就是 ∫ 1/u du 的形式嘛，积出来就是 ln|u|，也就是 ln|ln y| 啦。","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_091453"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^system:QQ联系人:岛岛(2926855205)发来了消息:为什么可以把1/y可以放进dy，这种操作的规则是？","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_091955"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^cyanAI:","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_092005"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^system:","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_092005"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^cyanAI:这个操作叫“凑微分”或者“第一类换元法”！\n规则其实就是微分定义的逆运算呀。\n\n你看，微分的定义是：d(f(x)) = f'(x) dx\n那反过来就是：f'(x) dx = d(f(x))\n\n因为 (ln y)' = 1/y\n所以我们就可以把 (1/y) * dy “打包”塞回去，写成 d(ln y) 啦。\n\n就像是把导数还原回原来的函数，然后放到 d 后面去~","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_092008"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^system:QQ联系人:岛岛(2926855205)发来了消息:[图片]\n^system:20260304_094840:这张图片的内容是：图片显示一张白纸上写有手写的数学题目。内容为：\n7.3","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_094840"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^cyanAI:","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_094859"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^system:","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_094859"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^cyanAI:这道题选 D 哦！\n是齐次微分方程，我们可以用换元法来做。\n\n1. 令 y = ux，那么 dy/dx = u + x(du/dx)\n2. 原方程化为：dy/dx = (x^3 + y^3) / (3xy^2)\n   代入 u 得到：u + x(du/dx) = (1 + u^3) / (3u^2)\n3. 移项化简：x(du/dx) = (1 - 2u^3) / (3u^2)\n4. 分离变量积分：∫ 3u^2 / (1 - 2u^3) du = ∫ dx/x\n   左边凑微分凑出 -1/2 * ln|1 - 2u^3|\n   右边是 ln|x| + C\n5. 整理后得到：1 - 2u^3 = C * x^(-2)\n6. 最后把 u = y/x 代回去，两边同乘 x^3，就得到 x^3 - 2y^3 = Cx 啦。","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_094904"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^system:QQ联系人:岛岛(2926855205)发来了消息:根本原理上，这类题是不是靠把齐次转换为x/y类的格式来解决？","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_100237"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^cyanAI:","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_100253"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^system:","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_100253"}
{"memory_state":{"R":1,"S":10,"last_T_distance":"10day","D":5,"a":1},"current":"^cyanAI:完全正确！岛岛抓住了问题的核心呢。\n\n齐次微分方程的本质特点，就是它的每一项关于 x 和 y 的次数都是一样的。\n利用这个性质，我们只要把分子分母同除以 x 的最高次幂，整个方程右边就一定能写成只包含 (y/x) 的形式，也就是 f(y/x)。\n\n这时候令 u = y/x，就能成功把原来没法分离的 x 和 y，转化成 u 和 x 的可分离变量方程啦。\n\n所以说，“构造出 y/x 并换元”就是解这类题的通解钥匙哦！","extraCurrent":{},"TIMESET":"20260304_100255"}
